item.title: Reflection - Heading into CS3216
item.description: CS3216: What I will learn In the Fall of 2019, I took a truly transformational class CS3216 at the National University of Singapore. The class is no ordinary class - it asks more of you, and gives more to you. At the start of the class, we were all asked to quickly write out our learning objectives in a written assignment. Though its raw and simple, I have reproduced that in the blog below.
